Class NotificationTypeServiceImp

java.lang.Object
eus.klimu.notification.domain.service.implementation.NotificationTypeServiceImp
All Implemented Interfaces:
NotificationTypeService
@Service
public class NotificationTypeServiceImp
extends java.lang.Object
implements NotificationTypeService
The implementation of the notification type service. It interacts with the different notification types using a notification type repository, modifying directly on the database.
